HEADWORD: Foregleam
<hw>Fore"gleam`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An antecedent or
premonitory gleam; a dawning light.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>foregleams</qex> of wisdom.</q>
